# FTP Uploader

## Description
Script for simplify the folder deployement onto several FTP servers

## Usage
ftpUpload folder/path

## Install
### cmd only
```sh
$ ./configure
$ sudo ./install
```
### cron job
```sh
$ not implemented
```

## Requirement
### Operating System
Linux

### Software
perl

### Library
libperl NET::TurboFTPSync
